dishes.name: Baked beans
dishes.description: Traditional baked beans made of soaked and boiled Piękny Jaś beans. Perfectly selected ingredients. Detailed description and step-by-step photos. I cordially invite you for the recipe for the best baked beans!

dishes.name: Chicken in puff pastry
dishes.description: Chicken in puff pastry is an interesting recipe for a delicious presentation of chicken fillets. Stuffing with spinach or mushrooms and cheese goes perfectly with delicate meat.

dishes.name: devolay
dishes.description: The de volaille cutlet, i.e. the classic Devolay with herb butter, is a delicious proposition for a special dinner. I invite you for my proven recipe for juicy chicken breast rolls.

dishes.name: Duvets
dishes.description: Kołduny are delicious dumplings stuffed with raw beef with onions and spices and cooked in boiling water. I invite you for my favorite and proven recipe.

dishes.name: Pork chops
dishes.description: Delicious pork chops in their own sauce is a great idea for dinner with the addition of Silesian dumplings or potato dumplings.

dishes.name: Stuffed potatoes
dishes.description: Stuffed potatoes are super delicious and extremely easy to make. My favorite version is potatoes stuffed with minced meat. This is the recipe I'm offering this time.

dishes.name: Gazpacho
dishes.description: Gazpacho is a delicious and super refreshing cold soup, which is prepared from raw tomatoes and other vegetables with the addition of olive oil and white bread. This recipe is perfect for coming and as a healthy and tasty meal every day.

dishes.name: Christmas sour soup
dishes.description: I invite you for my proven recipe for a delicious Christmas sour soup . This is a Lenten soup that I prepare on vegetable broth. Obligatory with dried mushrooms and rye sourdough.

dishes.name: Borscht
dishes.description: Red borscht is one of the most delicious Polish soups. My recipe for red borscht is very old and proven. I usually cook red borscht with potatoes for my family. Welcome!

dishes.name: Vegetable broth
dishes.description: It's good to know a good recipe for vegetable broth . Vegetable stock is the best base for soups and sauces. Such vegetable broth with the addition of several herbs and spices can also be divided into portions and frozen.

dishes.name: Pancakes on yogurt
dishes.description: Pancakes on yogurt with lots of apples are a delicious idea not only for breakfast but also for dinner. The recipe does not contain yeast, and you don't even need a mixer to make it.

dishes.name: Pistachio cheesecake
dishes.description: Pistachio cheesecake baked on a simple cookie base is an extremely delicious and unique pastry. I invite you for my favorite recipe that will work even for Christmas.
